Class DispatchingEventSource<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.opencredo.concursus.mapping.events.methods.dispatching.DispatchingEventSource<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - The type of the handler class.

    public class DispatchingEventSource<T>
extends Object
    Wraps an EventSource and dispatches replayed events to a suitable handler class.
